# UI Interactions

- Motion from `AppMotion`; routes from `page_transitions.dart`.
- Interactive surfaces use rounded theme shapes; `AppCard` for tappable cards.
- Confirm bars slide up with spring curve; page pushes use fade+slide.

Load `.cursor/skills/project/ui-interactions/SKILL.md` when adding buttons, cards, navigation, or animations.
